trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown if an error occurs during parsing of the Web Services Description Language (WSDL).
trans-unit.target: WSDL(Web Services Description Language)을 구문 분석하는 동안 오류가 발생하면 throw되는 예외입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException> is generated by the remoting WSDL parser.

The WSDL parser is used by the [Soapsuds Tool (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5), and can also be invoked programmatically using the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.MetaData> class.
trans-unit.target: WSDL 파서가에서 사용 되는 [Soapsuds 도구 (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5)를 사용 하 여 프로그래밍 방식으로 호출 될 수도 있습니다는 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.MetaData> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_EXCEPTION, which has the value 0x80131500.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException> 0x80131500 값이 있는 HRESULT COR_E_EXCEPTION를 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException>, see the <xref:System.Exception> constructors.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스에 대 한 초기 속성 값 목록은 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException>, 참조는 <xref:System.Exception> 생성자입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: throw되는 예외에 대해 serialize된 개체 데이터를 보유하는 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: 소스 또는 대상에 대한 컨텍스트 정보를 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SUDSParserException" /> class.
